WalSmart 🛒 – AI-powered Smart Shopping Assistant

WalSmart is a fully responsive, AI-enhanced web-based retail assistant inspired by Walmart. It predicts shopping needs, helps track essential refills, offers smart family sync features, and promotes sustainable choices — all from one clean interface.

## 🚀 Features
- 🔔 Predictive Reminders for common products
- 🛒 Smart Cart with bundled offers
- 💬 Conversational + Voice Assistant
- 👨‍👩‍👧 Family Mode with shared lists
- 🌱 Sustainability Tracker
- 🧑‍💻 Role-based Login/Register (Admin & Customer)
- 💬 Floating AI Chatbot with avatar support
- 🎨 Walmart-themed UI with background imagery

## 📁 Project Structure
