│ └── index.js
├── assets/
│ └── images/
│ ├── walmart-bg.jpg
│ └── chat-avatar.jpeg

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- HTML5 + CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)
- LocalStorage for user/session handling
- Mobile Responsive Layout
- No backend required — deploy-ready for GitHub Pages

